>"},{"pid":"b6e405126957a4529e651b76a96ed1f7ec00cf57","tid":2461672,"uid":262116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"小丑..."},{"pid":"fd08f3d6dd0435180740887ac3eadd83d30293d1","tid":2461672,"uid":143269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:09:53.000Z","msg":"我撐佢喎"},{"pid":"f64d54d30e928df62b27fe2f9296b43863924234","tid":2461672,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"笑撚左  變成車輪戰<br />\n鍾共頂得住先好呀  呀女"},{"pid":"b4a4cebd548dacd4ec411c7caf93037d18978d54","tid":2461672,"uid":262116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"422127481bb9840fe32fd25d90d22469e81c8d0c","tid":2461672,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"自從鍾培生與林作的拳賽落實於9月18日九龍灣Star Hall舉行、宣布門票索價最貴3萬元之後，網絡就此事的討論聲音不絕，繼日前燃燒到杜汶澤身上引起一輪罵戰之後，曾參選香港先生的Flow Leung（梁裕恆）又加入戰團，向鍾培生下戰書，揚言以100萬零1蚊兼讓單手：「K唔KO到要睇佢敢唔敢打。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxTS3cR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxTS3cR.jpg&h=a4e6f500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFlow向來對娛樂圈的大事很感興趣，參與討論密度甚高，而最近Flow就在鍾培生的Facebook Post下留言：「小丑，細路仔打交，單手都KO你。」隨即引起大量網民留言批評，豈料Flow再下一城，揚言出「K唔KO到要睇佢敢唔敢打。100萬零1蚊比（畀）佢，認真」。終於，鍾培生都出手回留言應戰，更連銀行戶口都公開叫Flow入數，並列出比賽細則：「就4月頭，入咗數話我知。」而培生亦有將Flow的留言分享至IG，並寫道：「我不嬲都唔係好覆傻仔，除非有着數。還掂都比（畀）錢搵緊sparring partner，留名等走數」。<br />\n<br />\n隨後Flow亦不甘示弱，在自己Facebook連開兩Post稱想應戰並將讓賽升級：「總之讓你單手單腳 唔帶頭套，打贏我100萬零1蚊，攞去，你輸左1蚊都唔洗攞出嚟。」而Flow又向《香港01》記者透露：「有朋友同我講，已經有人發起一人一蚊打x鍾培生，話已經有十幾萬人。不過我唔贊成咁嘅，呢條友咁黑人憎，我唔想人人發起眾籌從中取利，大家嚟留個言 留$1就夠 錢我一個出就夠。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxNHFZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyxNHFZY.jpg&h=7a189f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzRtByk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzRtByk.jpg&h=276b9efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDY0sE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDY0sE1.jpg&h=ee8c56d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsFiej3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsFiej3.jpg&h=14c05406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9E6huTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9E6huTp.jpg&h=7211063b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvNXuTr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvNXuTr.jpg&h=3f2fadae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3967Fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3967Fa.jpg&h=ef5412dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d45YYMR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd45YYMR.jpg&h=f5a92c8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"雖然唔鐘意終生<br />\n但哩條小丑點睇都無100萬"},{"pid":"94cd167f30b5bb5387516a93275e241c5d480348","tid":2461672,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"邊撚個<br />\n連二打六鍾共都應戰咁濫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0fefcb3d786a20066cbb1f62a6396cf3e67ffd","tid":2461672,"uid":236359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"不如battle royale 咁 一個島死鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5748fb91b924ddc6b3d70be89509adfee2b57af","tid":2461672,"uid":79126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"冇啦啦拎一百萬出嚟幫鍾共找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30534f93574cdac5c592158c1724358ce598d91","tid":2461672,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"一陣打到隻支畜要訓半年，咁儍仔林咪好著數？"},{"pid":"cb522b3853a2634fd